<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>Subpages should contain non-spoily information of the type currently contained in the on-line game help. Please put spoiler information in the appropriate place in the <a href="./SpoilerArchive">SpoilerArchive</a>.</strong></em> Thanks. <h2 id="head-272dd5bf44551ad953d069f65fecdbd13155a31e"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>Extra help for new players</h2>
Welcome to ToME!  <p>
ToME is a large, complex game with many choices to make. We recommend that you read the <a href="./Documentation">Documentation</a> to familiarize yourself with the game basics, with special attention to the following sections: 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fExploring_20the_Dungeon"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Exporing the Dungeon</a> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation/Fates"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Fates</a> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation#head-899bd694d29ace1be956ab35177075021977560b"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Guide to macros, keymaps and inscriptions</a> 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<p>
We also recommend that you read the the <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./FrequentlyAskedQuestions"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">ToME FAQ</a>, which contains many useful suggestions including good starting characters to try and recommended game options for beginners. 
</p>
<p>
Lastly, if you wish, you can also spoil yourself in the <a href="./SpoilerArchive">SpoilerArchive</a>.  
</p>
<p>
Welcome to our community. Good luck, and happy adventuring! If you need more help, please post in <a href="./GeneralDiscussion">GeneralDiscussion</a>; we will gladly do our best to help you. 
</p>
